---
import DisplayCards from './DisplayCards';
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative accent -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-sand to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="reveal max-w-2xl">
      <span class="font-body text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-terracotta">Who I am</span>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-heading font-bold text-navy leading-tight" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw + 0.5rem, 3rem);">
        Insider perspective,<br />
        <span class="text-slate/70">outsider thinking.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Bio text -->
      <div class="reveal space-y-5" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Why do some brands live rent-free in our heads — and how do they pay to be there? That question pulled me into marketing. Now I get to answer it at Charles Schwab, where I work on campaigns that reach millions of investors and advisors across the country.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          My day-to-day sits at the intersection of financial services, data, and marketing strategy — building operations that move faster and reach further.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Before Schwab, I spent 3+ years in Miami's agency world — running paid media, content strategy, and influencer programs for brands across B2B and B2C.
        </p>
        <p class="font-accent italic text-lg text-navy/70">
          Bilingual (English/Spanish). Miami-raised, FIU alum. Always up for a conversation about marketing strategy, financial services, or what makes a brand stick.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Display Cards — Interactive pillar showcase -->
      <div class="reveal flex items-center justify-center py-8" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
        <DisplayCards client:only="react" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
